Metadata-Version: 1.1
Name: replication-monitor
Version: 0.1.1
Summary: A GTK+ tool to create, delete and monitor CouchDB, AvanceDB, PouchDB and Cloudant replication jobs
Home-page: https://github.com/RipcordSoftware/avancedb-replication-monitor
Author: Craig Minihan, Ripcord Software
Author-email: craig@ripcordsoftware.com
License: MIT
Description: Replicate data between your CouchDB instances easily, for example:
        * replicate a single database to multiple targets, remote or local
        * replicate multiple databases to multiple targets
        * drag and drop a database to replicate it
        * drop the target database before replication
        * continuous replication
        * stored credentials and server details
Keywords: couchdb,pouchdb,avancedb,cloudant,replication
